      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WISHFUL THINKER (5) resumed for his second preparation with a fading on-pace third over 1200m at Kembla Grange in the heavy (9) conditions. Expected to have come on for that outing and can return to form quickly. Go close. RIGA (3) lost the rider on jumping over 1200m at this track on March 14. Deep into the prep and key jockey change from the good gate. Assess on his unlucky second at Newcastle over 1300m two-back. Races handy and capable of getting off the mark. STABILITY (4) three-year-old Zoustar gelding from the good mare Calming Influence on debut for the Dilmi stable. All three trials have been okay and the blinkers and lugging-bit go on. Stalks the good speed and must be considered. TIGLETTA (9) fourth-up today and jumps out in trip for the first time. Back in grade when she came out quickly from the outside gate before knocking up to finish sixth over 1100m at Goulburn. Place prospects best from the poor draw again.",
